            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="map-panel">
            <iframe 
                src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=8654%20S.%20113th%20West%20Ave.,%20Sapulpa,%20OK%2074066&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed" 
                allowfullscreen="" 
                loading="lazy" 
